  "body": "Since #4961, there is no way to use `rules.NewGroup` without registering the metrics twice, because the `metrics` field of `ManagerOptions` is not public.\r\n\r\nThis is a problem for Cortex, see https://github.com/cortexproject/cortex/pull/1154\r\n\r\nAny objections to making `metrics` and `newGroupMetrics` public?",
